title: Fiat Punto Mk1 Haynes Manual
description:
Fiat Punto Mk1 (1992-1999)
Service and repair manual

Models coverd:

Fiat Punto hatchback, including Selecta and special/limited editions.
Petrol engines: 1.1 litre (1108 cc) and 1.2 litre (1242 cc, 8-valve and 16-valve)
Diesel & turbo-diesel engines: 1.7 litre (1698 cc)

Does NOT cover 1.4 litre (1372 cc) or 1.6 litre (1581) petrol engines, or Cabriolet.
